preference.name: ARM_launch_mynavigator
preference.preference_description: Activates the rich client's launch My Teamcenter performance transaction. This measures the elapsed time for loading the "My Teamcenter" application. Valid Values: * ON: Enables performance monitoring of the launch My Teamcenter performance transaction. * OFF: Suppresses performance monitoring of the launch My Teamcenter performance transaction.
